你可以試下<br />
<pre><code data-type="">typedef struct{
    int b;
}goo;

int foo(const goo* a){
    ((goo*)a)-&gt;b++; // idiot!
    //a-&gt;b++;       // error: increment of member &lsquo;b&rsquo; in read-only object
}

int main()
{
    goo goo1;
    goo1.b = 0;
    foo(&amp;goo1);
    return 0;
}</code></pre><br />
若果唔係c++ 就唔會加static_cast,dynamic_cast,const_cast,reinterpret_cast做type casting。因為c既type casting就係咁。
